getScaledResources

public List<Scale.ScaledResource> getScaledResources(String path)
Returns an ordered series of scaled resources to try when loading an asset. The highest resolution will be tried first, then half that resolution and so forth down to a normal resolution image. In general this is simply 2, 1, but on a Retina iPad, it could be 4, 2, 1.
